name: Athletic Performance Advanced Program
description: 6 days per week workout program focused on athletic performance. Each session is 60-90 minutes.

exercises.name: EMOM: 1 Arm DB Press + Kettlebell Snatch
AMRAP: KB Swing + Kettlebell Bottoms-Up Press + Dumbbell Thrusters
AMRAP: Single-arm Overhead Carry + Reverse Lunge + Kettlebell Clean + DB Bench
EMOM: Cable Squat to Press + Overhead Extension
AMRAP: Kettlebell Swings + Dumbbell Swings + Kettlebell Windmill
AMRAP: Cable High Row + Kettlebell Gorilla Row
